bcunit
------------------------------------------
This is BCUnit, a fork of the defunct project CUnit, with several fixes and
patches applied.

Runtime requirements:
  cygwin-3.4.3-1
  libbcunit-devel-5.2.0-1bl1
  libbcunit1-5.2.0-1bl1
  libncursesw10-6.3-1.20220416
  pkg-config-1.9.3-1

Build requirements:
(besides corresponding -devel packages)
  binutils-2.39-1
  cmake-3.23.2-1
  cygport-0.35.5-1
  gcc-core-11.3.0-1
  gcc-g++-11.3.0-1
  libncurses-devel-6.3-1.20220416
  ninja-1.11.1-1

Canonical website:
  https://gitlab.linphone.org/BC/public/bcunit

Canonical download:
  https://gitlab.linphone.org/BC/public/bcunit/-/archive/5.2.0/bcunit-5.2.0.tar.bz2

-------------------------------------------

Build instructions:
  1. unpack bcunit-5.2.0-X-src.tar.xz
  2. if you use setup to install this src package,
     it will be unpacked under /usr/src automatically
        % cd /usr/src
        % cygport ./bcunit-5.2.0-X.cygport all

This will create:
  /usr/src/bcunit-5.2.0-X-src.tar.xz
  /usr/src/bcunit-5.2.0-X.tar.xz
  /usr/src/libbcunit1-5.2.0-X.tar.xz
  /usr/src/libbcunit-devel-5.2.0-X.tar.xz

-------------------------------------------

